@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/Unregistered User
CreateAccount : do/Get Valid User Credentials
CreateAccount : exit/User Account Registered

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry/Registered User
WatchVideos : do/Watch Videos
WatchVideos : exit/Watched Videos

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry/Registered User
UploadVideos : do/Upload Videos
UploadVideos : exit/Uploaded Videos

state "Save Videos" as SaveVideos
SaveVideos : entry/Registered User
SaveVideos : do/Save Videos
SaveVideos : exit/Saved Videos

state "View Saved Videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry/Registered User
ViewSavedVideos : do/View Saved Videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit/Viewed Saved Videos

state "Enter Discussion" as EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion : entry/Registered User
EnterDiscussion : do/Enter Discussion
EnterDiscussion : exit/Entered Discussion

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos
WatchVideos --> UploadVideos
UploadVideos --> SaveVideos
SaveVideos --> ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos --> EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion --> [*]

@enduml
